TextEng: How did I get here?
I need to return to my mission. I must get back to where I just was.
Text: 임무로 돌아가야 해요. 방금 있던 곳으로 다시 가야 합니다.

TextEng: How me get here?
Me need to return to mission. Me need to go back to place where me died.
Text: 나 임무로 돌아가야 해. 나 죽었던 곳으로 다시 가야 해.

TextEng: Goodbye.
I don't feel hurt at all. How was I healed?
Text: 전혀 안 다친 것 같아요. 어떻게 치료된 거죠?

TextEng: I don't want some stinking Word of Recall spell whisking me anywhere. Cancel the spell, right now!
Text: 더러운 귀환의 언령 주문으로 날 어디든 보내는 건 싫어요. 주문을 당장 취소하세요!

TextEng: Me not feel hurt at all. How me get healed?
Text: 나 전혀 안 다쳤어. 나 어떻게 치료됐어?

TextEng: Me no want Recall spell! Me want to control me own fate! Cancel spell now!
Text: 나 귀환 주문 싫어! 나 내 운명 스스로 결정하고 싶어! 주문 지금 취소해!

TextEng: Fine then! I still need to get back to where I was. Can you help with that?
Text: 좋아요! 그래도 전에 있던 곳으로 돌아가야 해요. 도와주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: Me not like that! But me accept it. Can you get me back to where me just was?
Text: 나 그거 싫어! 근데 받아들일게. 나 방금 있던 곳으로 돌려보내 줘?

TextEng: I want to go back to the place where I nearly died, and I want to go now!
Text: 거의 죽을 뻔했던 곳으로 다시 가고 싶어요. 지금 당장요!

TextEng: Me want go back to spot where me almost die! Me want go right now!
Text: 나 거의 죽었던 곳으로 다시 가고 싶어! 나 지금 가고 싶어!

TextEng: I need to prepare before I resume my mission. I'll see you later.
Text: 임무를 재개하기 전에 준비가 필요해요. 나중에 뵙겠습니다.

TextEng: Me need prepare stuff before me continue mission. Goodbye.
Text: 나 임무 계속하기 전에 준비해야 해. 안녕.

TextEng: Yes. Transport me there now.
Yes. Me want to go back now.
I've changed my mind. I'll see you later.
Me change my mind. Goodbye.
Who are you?
Who you be?
Ummm... when did you cast this Word of Recall spell on me?
Text: 음... 언제 이 귀환의 언령 주문을 저한테 거신 거예요?

TextEng: When you cast Recall spell on me?
Text: 너 언제 나한테 귀환 주문 걸었어?

TextEng: Me need healing.
I need healing.
Who you be?
Who are you?
Me not understand 'bout Stone of Recall and teleport portal.
Text: 나 귀환석이랑 순간이동 차원문 이해 못 해.

TextEng: Teleportation portal? Stone of Recall? I don't understand.
Text: 순간이동 차원문이요? 귀환석이요? 무슨 말인지 모르겠어요.

TextEng: That be big power magic!
That's some pretty powerful magic!
That's handy.
Me need you go over that one more time.
Can you explain that again?
Why, what yous mean by that?
Why, what do you mean?
Teleport portal? Recall Stone? What you be talking about?
Teleportation portal? Stone of Recall? What are you talking about?
That's handy.
Me want go back where me last use Recall Stone.
Text: 나 귀환석 마지막으로 쓴 곳으로 돌아가고 싶어.

TextEng: I want to go back to where I last used my Stone of Recall.
Text: 귀환석을 마지막으로 사용한 곳으로 돌아가고 싶어요.
